CHANGE LOG 

27th January 2016

	- Login now completely works, up to you to make a styling.
	- Added a db_rel table that is basically the relationship between 2 users ( blocked/friend ).
	- Added a db_friend_req table that manages friend requests
	- Relation model created ( for blocked, friends, friendlists and adding friend / blocing people feature)
	- Made a change for $_SESSION['username'] to $_SESSION['ifitness_id'].
	- Added a default null function for Gender in Register to avoid people not filling it up.
	- Many fixes in the USER Model, All the functions in there were tested and work properly now.